FIG. 1 is a schematic diagram of a prior art control system connected to a DC brushless motor;


FIG. 2 is a schematic diagram of a control system in accordance with the present invention connected to a DC brushless motor;


FIG. 3 is a graph showing the variation in the proportional contribution made by each of two signals to a combined measurement of the speed of the motor, over a range of motor speeds, according to a first preferred weighting scheme; and


FIG. 4 is a graph showing the variation in the proportional contribution made by each of two signals to a combined measurement of the speed of the motor, over a range of motor speeds, according to a second preferred weighting scheme.
